Here is the proper mask to wear when sandblasting, grinding, playing
around with asbesto's or just sanding--Available at any better body shop
supply house.
3-M # 7182 or 7183.
$30.00 bucks

And this is not just some BS from me--
I just got done calling 3-M.
You won't find it on any web page.
This is the mask that I use for any of the above.

